Lár DMN: Abstract Blueprint for Domain-Specific Continual Learning Memory
Copyright 2025-2026 Aadithya Vishnu Sajeev

This product includes software developed by Snath AI.

This repository provides a domain-agnostic blueprint for continual learning
memory, demonstrating concepts such as:
- Three-Tier Memory Architecture (Episodic / Semantic / Procedural)
- HMAC-Signed Durable Artifact Pipeline (failure-class centroids + LoRA adapters)
- Inference-Time Divergence Routing (System 1 centroid match / System 2 LoRA injection)

Built on published prior art: DOI 10.5281/zenodo.20278781 (DAS),
10.5281/zenodo.20278775 (UCR), 10.5281/zenodo.20581128 (LTL),
10.5281/zenodo.20614051 (EIM), 10.5281/zenodo.20682615 (PAV).